# This folder IS the live HERMES_HOME (bind-mounted). Ignore top-level entries
# (anchored /* so it doesn't recurse into re-included dirs), then re-include the
# curated files + all of skills/cs2 (ours and the skills Hermes writes). Bundled
# skills and runtime state (memory, sessions, node/, caches, .env) stay ignored.
/*
!/.gitignore
!/SOUL.md
!/USER.md
!/AGENTS.md
!/config.yaml
!/skills/
/skills/*
!/skills/cs2/

